ineering services, such as product engineering, product re-engineering, sheet metal-BIW design and engineering, and jigs and fixture services, as well as reverse engineering and legacy data conversion. In addition, the company offers manufacturing services comprising tool room, and prototype and mass manufacturing services, as well as contract engineering manpower for onsite and offsite deployment. Further, it provides engineering and designing software services and business solutions. Autoline Industries Limited was founded in 1995 and is based in Pune, India."}}